---
description: Project-wide conventions
alwaysApply: true
---
- Read AGENTS.md before acting. The golden rules there are binding.
- Retrieval is shared; do not duplicate PubMed access logic.
- All model calls go through biolit.core.llm. Never import anthropic/openai/google SDKs elsewhere.
- Config-driven, not hard-coded. Async for network I/O. Structured logging only.
- Finish a task only when ruff, mypy, and pytest pass and there is a runnable check.
